  "A": [
    To what extent does the hardware platform #footnote[Server, PC, and Raspberry Pi] impacts the energy efficiency of code generated by LLMs? See footnotes #footnote[Even tho this is not an explicit research question of the paper, the impact of the hardware platform is a recurring theme of this research.].
